                        10. <b>Performance Management:</b> Establish clear performance expectations aligned with organizational objectives. Regularly monitor and evaluate employee performance through reviews, feedback sessions, and goal tracking. Offer constructive feedback, recognition, and rewards to motivate and engage employees.
